      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist's dream, powered by the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 that screams to an 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers crisp, rev-matched downshifts, paired with a variable M differential lock for surgical corner exits. This example features the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable suspension geometry and has had critical preventative maintenance performed, including rod bearings and throttle valve actuators. The chassis rigidity and near 50/50 weight distribution provide an analog driving experience that modern turbocharged platforms simply cannot replicate. A mechanically sound, driver-spec machine ready for the canyons.",
